「LIKE AND COMMENT 3X FOR A TBH & RATE」
A small female walks the streets at night, hoping for someone to take her in. She'd just escaped her abuse-filled past, and is now trying a place to stay. She runs into a lean man, one she knew. He was a boy she went to school with, and who was willing to take her in. There, she began to become stronger, a better version of herself. ----------------------------------------------------------
Rosanne Kim is a twenty two year old sweetheart who moved to Seoul with an old friend after she escaped her abusive boyfriend. She spent one year in a dance academy, where she graduated top of her class. She later left the school to live a much simpler life in an apartment in southern Seoul. She hasn't met the one yet, and is weary of starting new friend ships. She's 5'2 but she likes to act taller. If you giver her hugs and call her baby, she'll melt at your finger tips. Taken by @kjng.alex

Learn more about us and our upcoming events on our website!

Centramos nuestra visión, en la Armonía de Planeta Tierra y todos los que habitan en ella.
